==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Powerless
<hw>Pow"er*less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Destitute of power, force, or
energy; weak; impotent; not able to produce any effect.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Pow"er*less*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Pow"er*less*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Powldron</ent>⟦br⟧
